{"word":"πρῶτος","slug":"πρῶτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πρῶτος, η, ον</el></b> [the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ superl.\">superl.</a> of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a></el>] the basic idea: having to do with beforeness<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘having primary position in a sequence’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> temporally, <b>first, earlier, earliest <a href='B:470 12:45'>Mt 12:45</a>; <a href='B:470 19:30'>19:30</a>; <a href='B:470 20:8'>20:8</a>, <a href='B:470 20:10'>10</a>; <a href='B:470 26:17'>26:17</a>; <a href='B:480 13:10'>Mk 13:10</a>; <a href='B:480 16:9'>16:9</a>; <a href='B:500 1:15'>J 1:15</a>, <a href='B:500 1:30'>30</a>; <a href='B:500 20:4'>20:4</a>, <a href='B:500 20:8'>8</a>; <a href='B:510 20:18'>Ac 20:18</a>; <a href='B:510 26:23'>26:23</a>; <a href='B:520 10:19'>Ro 10:19</a>; <a href='B:530 14:30'>1 Cor 14:30</a>; <a href='B:570 1:5'>Phil 1:5</a>; <a href='B:610 2:13'>1 Ti 2:13</a>; <a href='B:610 5:12'>5:12</a>; <a href='B:620 4:16'>2 Ti 4:16</a>; <a href='B:650 8:7'>Hb 8:7</a>, <a href='B:650 8:13'>13</a>; <a href='B:650 9:15'>9:15</a>; <a href='B:680 2:20'>2 Pt 2:20</a>; <a href='B:690 4:19'>1 J 4:19</a>; <a href='B:730 1:17'>Rv 1:17</a>; <a href='B:730 2:4'>2:4f</a>, 19; <a href='B:730 21:1'>21:1</a>, <a href='B:730 21:4'>4</a>.</b> Nt. as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a>, <el>πρῶτον</el>, <b>first <a href='B:470 5:24'>Mt 5:24</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> <el>τὸ πρῶτον</el> the first time <b><a href='B:500 10:40'>J 10:40</a>;</b> at first <b><a href='B:500 12:16'>12:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on sequence in enumeration <b>first <a href='B:470 17:27'>Mt 17:27</a></b> (very first); <b><a href='B:470 21:28'>21:28</a>; <a href='B:470 22:25'>22:25</a>; <a href='B:470 27:64'>27:64</a>; <a href='B:480 12:20'>Mk 12:20</a>; <a href='B:490 2:2'>Lk 2:2</a>; <a href='B:490 14:18'>14:18</a>